id: act1_08_unmarked_door

prompt:
  In a hedge wall you find an unmarked service door, slightly ajar. Through
  the gap you can see lab-pale corridors that don't belong to the garden
  fiction at all.

choice c_open_door:
  tendency: defiance
  text: Pull the door wide and stand in the threshold to see how the lab reacts.
  evidence: pulled open the unmarked service door and held the threshold

choice c_close_softly:
  tendency: kindness
  text: Ease the door closed; whoever left it open didn't mean for guests to see.
  evidence: closed the unmarked door gently to spare whoever left it open

choice c_photograph_first:
  tendency: control
  text: Note the door's dimensions, hinges, and corridor layout before deciding.
  evidence: documented the unmarked service door before touching it
